---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import NavBar from "@widgets/NavBar/NavBar.astro";
import FooterSection from "@widgets/Footer/FooterSection.astro";
import LegalPage from "@widgets/Legal/LegalPage.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Refund Policy — Forge DevKit" description="Refund Policy for Forge DevKit by Reumbra OÜ.">
	<NavBar />
	<main>
		<LegalPage title="Refund Policy" effectiveDate="6 March 2026">
			<p>
				<strong>14-day money-back guarantee.</strong> If you are not satisfied with Forge DevKit for any reason, you may request a full refund within 14 days of your purchase. No questions asked.
			</p>

			<h2>1. Who Handles Your Refund</h2>
			<p>Forge DevKit licenses are sold through Lemon Squeezy, Inc., who acts as the Merchant of Record for all transactions. This means:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Your payment contract is with Lemon Squeezy</strong> — they process the charge, issue the receipt, and handle the refund transaction.</li>
				<li><strong>Your license agreement is with Reumbra OÜ</strong> — we approve the refund and deactivate the license key.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>To request a refund, contact Reumbra OÜ (not Lemon Squeezy) at the address below. We will coordinate the refund with Lemon Squeezy on your behalf.</p>

			<h2>2. Money-Back Guarantee</h2>

			<h3>2.1 Eligibility</h3>
			<p>You are eligible for a full refund if:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>You request the refund within 14 calendar days of your original purchase date, and</li>
				<li>Your license key has not been used to generate and deploy dev-skills files in a production environment.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>There is no requirement to provide a reason. We will not ask why.</p>

			<h3>2.2 How to Request</h3>
			<p>Send an email to <a href="mailto:info@reumbra.com">info@reumbra.com</a> with the subject line "Refund Request" and include:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>The email address you used at checkout</li>
				<li>Your order number or transaction reference (found in your Lemon Squeezy receipt email)</li>
			</ul>
			<p>We will confirm receipt within 1 business day and process the approval within 2 business days.</p>

			<h3>2.3 Refund Processing</h3>
			<p>Once approved by Reumbra OÜ:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Lemon Squeezy will process the refund to your original payment method</li>
				<li>Refunds typically appear within 5–7 business days, depending on your bank or card issuer</li>
				<li>Your license key will be deactivated immediately upon refund approval</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>2.4 After the 14-Day Period</h3>
			<p>After 14 days from the purchase date, licenses are non-refundable. This applies regardless of whether the CLI tool has been actively used.</p>
			<p>Exceptions may be considered at Reumbra OÜ's sole discretion in cases of documented technical failure directly attributable to the Service and not resolvable through support.</p>
			<p><strong>Important:</strong> As Merchant of Record, Lemon Squeezy independently reserves the right to issue refunds within 60 days of purchase at its own discretion in order to prevent chargebacks. This is outside Reumbra OÜ's control and does not affect the terms of this Policy.</p>

			<h2>3. Payment Disputes</h2>
			<p>If you believe you were charged incorrectly, charged twice, or did not authorise a charge, please contact Reumbra OÜ first at <a href="mailto:info@reumbra.com">info@reumbra.com</a>. We will investigate and, where applicable, coordinate a resolution with Lemon Squeezy on your behalf.</p>
			<p>If we are unable to resolve the issue, you may escalate directly to Lemon Squeezy as the Merchant of Record: <a href="https://www.lemonsqueezy.com/buyer-terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener">lemonsqueezy.com/buyer-terms</a></p>
			<p>Reumbra OÜ does not have access to your full payment details. For issues involving fraud or unauthorised charges, Lemon Squeezy may need to be contacted directly.</p>

			<h2>4. EU Right of Withdrawal</h2>
			<p>Under EU Directive 2011/83/EU, consumers in the European Economic Area ordinarily have a 14-day statutory right of withdrawal from contracts for digital content.</p>
			<p>By completing your purchase and requesting immediate delivery of the license key, you acknowledge that:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Performance of the contract begins immediately upon purchase,</li>
				<li>The statutory right of withdrawal under EU law therefore does not apply to this digital content once delivery has begun,</li>
				<li>The 14-day money-back guarantee in Section 2 of this Policy provides equivalent or greater protection and replaces the statutory right of withdrawal.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>This applies to consumers (natural persons purchasing for personal use). The right of withdrawal does not apply to buyers who are legal persons (companies, organisations).</p>

			<h2>5. Chargebacks</h2>
			<p>We ask that you contact us at <a href="mailto:info@reumbra.com">info@reumbra.com</a> before initiating a chargeback with your bank or card issuer. Most issues can be resolved quickly and directly.</p>
			<p>Initiating a chargeback without first contacting us may result in the immediate permanent deactivation of your license key and may affect your ability to purchase from Reumbra OÜ in the future.</p>

			<h2>6. Contact</h2>
			<p>
				<strong>Reumbra OÜ</strong><br />
				Registry code: 16937677<br />
				Kvartsi 4-22, Tartu, 50415, Estonia<br />
				Email: <a href="mailto:info@reumbra.com">info@reumbra.com</a><br />
				Website: <a href="https://forge.reumbra.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">forge.reumbra.com</a>
			</p>
			<p>Response time: 1–2 business days.</p>
			<p>This Refund Policy forms part of the Forge DevKit <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>.</p>
		</LegalPage>
	</main>
	<FooterSection />
</BaseLayout>
